{
  "stem": "5970.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my best friend, who is now in Israel, came with a-- with a-- with a-- a cup of soup for me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she thought she was doing me such a big favor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I came from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had food there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I'd-- it wasn't-- she probably took away her-- her last ration from-- from her, and she brought it for me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I met my mother there, but only very briefly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they stayed in that camp, and I was chosen with the other 100, among the 100, to another camp in Auschwitz, which was called the Musterlager.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, the Musterlager, it was there as an example.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a-- it was like a showpiece for-- if, in the case, a-- a-- a Red Cross delegation would come.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I never saw one, but they said they-- they used to come there before because they kept prisoners of wars and German prisoners there as well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took the 100 of us, and we came to this big gate there with the-- with this 'Arbeit macht frei' sign, and we were put into barracks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These barracks were much better and cleaner than the ones in the other camp in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put in there, and we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the work was-- again, the standing from 5 o'clock in the morning, and it was starting to get cold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- it was starting to get cold, and it was-- all-- all I remember is the cold and the hunger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were in the street the whole day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The group that I was with, the 100, were divided in 10 again, and we were called Strassenkommando.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It means we worked in the streets.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
